QA Technician (FISHER/201303/03/SG)
Job ID
EPM-00004349
Country
Singapore
State/Province
Singapore
City
Singapore
Publish Start Date
Mar 19 2013
Job Level
Experienced (Non-Manager)
|
Responsibilities:
Ensure all measuring equipments use in the factory is working to its specific requirement.
Schedule & calibrate measuring & test equipment, ensure all measuring & test equipment are performing to its intended requirements.
Perform first article inspection.
Perform other quality related activities assigned by supervisor.
Look for continuous improvement & pro-active in all areas.
Participate in cost saving project.
Conduct yearly refresher training & certification for QA Inspector.
Requirements:
Nitec in Mechanical/SPM 5 credits with some technical certification with minimum 2 years experience in QA.
Able to communicate well with others, understand & speaks good English.
Able to read blue-prints & familiar with dimensional measuring equipment.
Good understanding on Geometric Dimensioning & Tolerance (GD&T).
Able to use CMM & Smartscope.